qFileTime.desc:
Last modified time stamp of the app.
This property is only used with Qlik Sense desktop.
Is set to 0 for Qlik Sense server.

qFileSize.desc:
Size of remote app.
This property is only used with Qlik Sense desktop.
Is set to 0 for Qlik Sense server.

qDocId.desc:
Identifier of the app.

In local installation mode, the identifier is the path and name of the app
In server mode, the identifier is the app's GUID.

qMeta.desc: Meta data related to the app.

qLastReloadTime.desc: Last reload time of the app.

qReadOnly.desc: If set to true, it means that the app is read-only.
